SOFTWARE INSTALLATION

Actions with RPM

rpm -ivh name.rpm --- Install

rpm -e name --- Erase

rpm -Uvh name --- Upgrade

rpm -q name --- Query

rpm -V name --- Verify

Actions with YUM

 /etc/yum.repos.d
 
 /etc/yum.repos.d/redhat.repo
 
 /etc/yum.repos.d/nginx.pepo
 
 yum install httpd
 
 yum repolist
 
 yum provides name
 
 yum remove name
 
 yum update name
 
 yum update
 
 Actions with DPKG
 
 dpkg -i name --- Install
 
gpkg -r --- Remove

dpkg -l name --- List

dpkg -s --- Status

dpkg -V --- Verify 
 
 Actions with APT & APT-GET

/etc/zpt/sources.list

apt update --- Обновить список пакетов

apt upgrade --- Обновить установленные пакеты

apt edit-sources --- Изменить файл репозиториев

apt install --- Установить/Обновит пакет

apt remove --- Удалить пакет

apt search --- Искать пакет

apt list --- Список пакетов

apt list | grep name





























